 add-ons and updates will be free.<br><br>- The game can be played with 1, 2, 3 or 4 people.<br><br>- There are 4 different character appearances.<br><br>- There are different features that the character uses while fighting.<br><br>- Each map has a different atmosphere.<br><br>- The game is played on a 16:9 wide screen.<br><br>- Developed with Unreal Engine 5.2<br><br>- It is played with keyboard and mouse.<br><br>- The camera style is played as &quot;Third Person&quot;.<br><br>- For best performance, the necessary DirectX must be installed and your graphics card driver must be up to date.<br><br>- The game duration varies depending on the player.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111330/extras/steam_aciklama_2.jpg?t=1728553012\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Conqueror of the Zodon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3111330/33a81094af4778d2a39bc25cbd5ea26cd7aeef89.jpg"},{"name":"Savior of the Moon City","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3111330/76ddc5746046e5a81dcf40c1ae9fc8d930b11b56.jpg"},{"name":"Savior of the C.O.M.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3111330/9713d34e7d18260a5ec82b7fa1daa069117cc3d0.jpg"},{"name":"Conqueror of the High Tower","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3111330/f1899c4807dc791e279ba2a7e1e31cfc49dd1f5b.jpg"},{"name":"Conqueror of the Leaviriar","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3111330/32ef57a6de2480a4f7f5854cd1949227fca6f23f.jpg"},{"name":"Guardian of the Orman","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3111330/489df104a7227fd7c180ee0474d394f06065ad6e.jpg"},{"name":"Guardian of the Lina","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3111330/8a591b99d4c74e828e3092321a343e940a043de2.jp